Class
Description
Activity

Conflict
This interface defines a method for checking conflicts between activities.
ConflictException
Represents an exception that is thrown when a conflict is encountered within a schedule.

Represents a Course within the university's scheduling system.

Utility class for reading and writing Course records from/to text files.
Event
Represents an event with a title, meeting days, start time, end time, and event details.
WolfScheduler
Manages the scheduling of courses for a user, including maintaining a course catalog, creating and modifying schedules, and exporting schedules to files.
